! Mia Denyigba Lɔ̃lɔ̃ la
|-
! colspan="2" bgcolor="red" |<span style="color:White">First stanza</span>
|-
|width=2%|
<center>
Mia denyigba lɔ̃lɔ̃ la<br />
Enu wonye woa ƒoa sia?<br />
Mia tɔgbuiwo tsɔ woƒe<br />
agbe gble ɖe eta xɔe nami<br />
Eɖo nye kpli woha dzi<br />
be mia wɔ miatɔ sinu<br />
Nuvevi nyenye, diɖoɖo,<br />
kple ame ɖokui tɔdzidzi,<br />
Bu miaƒe azɔli hegble mia denyigba alegbegbe.<br />
</center> 
|-
!colspan="2" bgcolor="yellow"|<span style="color:Black">Second stanza</span>
|-
|width=2%|
<center>
Agbalemenunya ƒuƒlu<br />
Loo hotsui kpɔkpɔ guduu<br />
Kple agbe yaka nɔnɔ<br />
Meyina kple anyigba lɔ̃lɔ̃ o<br />
Ta bɔbɔ kple amelɔame<br />
Nyui didi na amesiame<br />
Kple lã dodo ame ɖokui<br />
Na xɔ̃lɔ̃ viviwo ƒe nyonyo ko<br />
Woawo mee tomefafa<br />
Kple ŋgɔyiyi nyui wodzɔ tso.<br />
</center>
|-
!colspan="2" bgcolor="green"|<span style="color:White">Chorus</span>
|-
|width=2%|
<center>
Denyigba wo nyonyo<br />
Denyigba wo gbegble<br />
Alesi newɔe la<br />
Sigbe ke woa nɔ daa<br />
</center>
